mintydocs-noparentpage:
An error message. Parameters:
 $1 - a page type
mintydocs-invalidparentpage:
An error message. Parameters:
* $1 - a page name
* $2 - a page type
mintydocs-product-versionlist: A header above a list of links for different versions of some product.
mintydocs-version-desc:
A header for a page about one version of a product. Parameters:
* $1 - a version number
* $2 - a product name
mintydocs-version-manuallist: A header for a list of instruction manuals.
mintydocs-manual-desc:
A descriptive header for a page that is an instruction manual. Parameters:
* $1 - a version number
* $2 - a product name
mintydocs-manual-otherversions: Read this manual for other versions:
mintydocs-manual-contents: A header above a table of contents.
mintydocs-topic-desc:
A header for a page about one topic. Parameters:
* $1 - a manual name
*2 - a version number
* $3 - a product name
mintydocs-topic-otherversions: Read this topic for other versions:
mintydocs-publish-button: Text of a button that will "publish" some pages, i.e. copy them from the "Draft" namespace to the main namespace
mintydocs-publish-singlepage: Text before a button to publish a single page
mintydocs-publish-success:
Message displayed after one or more pages have been "published". Parameters:
* $1 - a list of wiki pages
mintydocs-publish-editsummary: The edit summary for any page that gets "published".
mintydocs-createdraft-button: Text of a button that will copy some pages from the main namespace to the "Draft" namespace.
mintydocs-createdraft-singlepage: Text before a button to create a page in the "Draft" namespace
mintydocs-createdraft-success:
Message displayed after one or more pages in the "Draft" namespace have been created. Parameters:
* $1 - a list of wiki pages
mintydocs-createdraft-editsummary: The edit summary for any page created in the "Draft" namespace
mintydocs-copy-button:
Text of a button to copy some pages from one location to another.
{{Identical|Copy}}
mintydocs-copy-singlepage: Text before a button to create a page that is a copy of another page
mintydocs-copy-success:
Message displayed after one or more pages have been copied elsewhere. Parameters:
* $1 - a list of wiki pages
mintydocs-copy-editsummary: The edit summary when a page is saved that is a copy of another page
mintydocs-delete-deletionreason: The reason given when a page is deleted because it is contained in a "Manual" that is deleted
mintydocs-tocinput-rename: Text of a dropdown menu choice
mintydocs-tocinput-changetype: Text of a dropdown menu choice
